[
    {
        "page": 1,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "The sun was already high, painting warm stripes across the sidewalk as you rushed toward school, bag bouncing against your side. Late again.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 2,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "You could already hear the bell tolling in the distance\u2014your internal clock always five minutes behind, your legs always five steps too slow.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 3,
        "speaker": "Sayori",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            90,
            -40
        ],
        "text": "Wait up!!",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 4,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Sayori's voice cut through the breeze. You barely turned before she caught up, half-jogging, half-laughing, a pink blur of energy and determination.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 5,
        "speaker": "Sayori",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            90,
            -40
        ],
        "text": "You're not in a club, right? Please say no.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 6,
        "speaker": "MC",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Technically\u2026",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 7,
        "speaker": "Sayori",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            90,
            -40
        ],
        "text": "Perfect! You're coming with me. Performance Studies Club. It'll be fun. Harumi says we're doing something new today!",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 8,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Before you could protest, she was already pulling you across campus like a kite on a string.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 9,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "The clubroom was tucked into the quiet end of the building. Inside, sunlight spilled across scattered sheet music and scuffed floors. A piano sat in the corner like an old friend.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 10,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "A girl with a clipboard looked up from her notes.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 11,
        "speaker": "Tiffany",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            120,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "You must be our new member.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 12,
        "speaker": "Tiffany",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            120,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "This is the Performance Studies Club. We explore movement, voice, and music as a form of self-expression. Every Friday, we perform something new\u2014structured, original, or interpretive.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 13,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Before you could respond, someone flipped over a desk and landed in front of you with a dramatic pose.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 14,
        "speaker": "Harumi",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            60,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "Or in normal-people terms, we sing, we dance, and we occasionally cry on purpose. It's awesome.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 15,
        "speaker": "Harumi",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            60,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "Basically, think talent show but way cooler.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 16,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "A voice drifted lazily from the window.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 17,
        "speaker": "Cassian",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            160,
            -20
        ],
        "text": "Don't forget the weekly identity crises.",
        "inputs": [],
        "character": "cassian",
        "pose": "1",
        "face_parts": [
            "1",
            "1",
            "4",
            "1"
        ]
    },
    {
        "page": 18,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "You turned. Leaning against the windowsill was a boy with tousled hair and an unreadable smile. Cassian.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 19,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "He looked at you like you were already predictable. And in the corner, curled up around a faded pink pillow, was a girl who hadn't spoken.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 20,
        "speaker": "Harumi",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            60,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "That's Hanami. She's quiet. Don't push her.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 21,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "You introduced yourself\u2014formally, or sarcastically, or not at all. Either way, it was too late to back out.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 22,
        "speaker": "Harumi",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            60,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "Since you're new, I'll show you how it's done.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 23,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "She queued up a track on her phone and exploded into motion\u2014claps, steps, twirls, a pirouette that ended in a wink.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 24,
        "speaker": "Harumi",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            60,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "Try to keep up.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 25,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "You stepped in. Maybe you crushed it. Maybe you tripped. Either way, you earned a reaction.",
        "inputs": [],
        "type": "game",
        "game_number": 1
    },
    {
        "page": 26,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Harumi whooped or teased. Cassian smirked or shrugged. Tiffany jotted something down. Hanami didn't move.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 27,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Next, Tiffany took the piano. Her fingers moved like clock hands, precise and polished. A soft waltz filled the room.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 28,
        "speaker": "Tiffany",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            120,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "Now you.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 29,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Maybe you tried. Maybe you hesitated. Either way, she nodded\u2014understanding or not.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 30,
        "speaker": "Tiffany",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            120,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "Hanami?",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 31,
        "speaker": "Hanami",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            40,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Not today.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 32,
        "speaker": "Harumi",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            60,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "No problem.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 33,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Cassian walked to the center of the room. No music. Just a slow breath.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 34,
        "speaker": "Cassian",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            160,
            -20
        ],
        "text": "We perform because we're afraid of being invisible.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 35,
        "speaker": "Cassian",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            160,
            -20
        ],
        "text": "We lie loudly. We bleed quietly. We smile when we mean scream.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 36,
        "speaker": "Cassian",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            160,
            -20
        ],
        "text": "Your turn.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 37,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Maybe you matched his tempo. Maybe you stumbled. Either way, he gave you a verdict.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 38,
        "speaker": "Cassian",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            160,
            -20
        ],
        "text": "You listen.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 39,
        "speaker": "Cassian",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            160,
            -20
        ],
        "text": "Or: You're part of the noise.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 40,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "The spotlight was yours now. You stepped forward. You breathed in. You performed.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 41,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Maybe you soared. Or maybe your fingers slipped. Either way, the room reacted.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 42,
        "speaker": "Tiffany",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/clubroom.png",
        "position": [
            120,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "Good start.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 43,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/school_path.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "After the club, the sky burned gold behind the trees. The others packed up, chatting and teasing. You lingered by the doorway.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 44,
        "speaker": "Tiffany",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/school_path.png",
        "position": [
            120,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "Next meeting's tomorrow. Bring ideas. Bring heart.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 45,
        "speaker": "Harumi",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/school_path.png",
        "position": [
            60,
            -30
        ],
        "text": "And bring snacks.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 46,
        "speaker": "Cassian",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/school_path.png",
        "position": [
            160,
            -20
        ],
        "text": "*two-finger salute*",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 47,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/school_path.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Hanami slipped out without a word, her pillow still clutched tightly.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 48,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/school_path.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "You thought about following someone home... Tiffany, Cassian, or no one at all.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 49,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "Somewhere down the path, a flyer fluttered on a telephone pole.",
        "inputs": []
    },
    {
        "page": 50,
        "speaker": "",
        "background": "assets/backgrounds/residential.png",
        "position": [
            0,
            0
        ],
        "text": "\u201cPERFORMANCE,\u201d it read in bold, black ink. Beneath it, scribbled by hand: If you mess up, do it loud enough to matter.",
        "inputs": []
    }
]